comments: Henson (DET) is firming up and makes marginal contact with Ariza (POR) while setting the pick.

Snell (DET) slightly extends his leg into Anthony (POR) on the jump shot attempt.

Snell (DET) briefly extends his arms into Ariza (POR) while setting the screen.
Ariza (POR) establishes a position and makes slight contact with Rose (DET) during his shot attempt.
Whiteside (POR) cleanly blocks Rose's (DET) shot attempt, any additional contact is deemed incidental.
Galloway (DET) slightly extends his leg into Trent (POR) during his shot attempt.
Mykhailiuk (DET) commits a take foul on McCollum (POR).
Galloway (DET) commits a take foul on McCollum (POR).

Trent Jr. (POR) maintains a legal guarding position on Galloway (DET) and cleanly intercepts the pass. Any additional contact is deemed incidental.
